title: Australian V8 Supercars - 2013 - Ipswitch
description:
Part 1 [Saturday July 27th-2013] The V8 Supercars are at Queensland Raceway for the Coates Hire Ipswich 360. This file includes  coverage of Qualifying for Race 22 as well as all the support race action from the Touring Car Masters and the Dunlop development Series (Race 1).
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
A friend of mine in the netherlands can only recieve a "Highlights" version broadcast of the Australian V8 Supercars. So I will be recording these and sharing with both him and the world.
PLEASE SEED!!!
If you cant get enough of the V8 Supercars or love motor racing in general, why not try virtual racing on the worlds best public raciunig simulator: iRacing. www.iracing.com
